title: Bucs Lose Again, Expectations For CMC
description:
Welcome back to (debatable) with hosts Pablo Torre and Domonique Foxworth featuring Mina Kimes! On today’s show: What's the biggest takeaway from the Ravens' win over the Bucs? Which team would your perception of change more with a win this weekend: the Seahawks or the Giants? What’s the bigger story: the Chiefs trading for Kadarius Toney or Ja’Marr Chase being out for 4-6 weeks with a hip injury? How do you expect the 49ers offense to look going forward with Christian McCaffrey? Plus, Aaron Rodgers and Russell Wilson continue to get on their teammates' nerves!
